# Hangman-OS - User Manual
Danger, danger, danger! There is danger in the Operating System and Hangman-OS needs your help. 
Play the Classic Hangman game and defeat the viruses by correctly finding out six coded kill codes to save your operating system.

##Objective
The goal of the game is to correctly get the letters of the hidden words with only 6 tries, get six correct guesses to win the game.

##Game Rules
1. A random word is selected at the start of the game.
2. The word displayed by using underscores (_), shows how many letters there are in the word.
3. For each word, you only get six lives to survive.
4. Guess incorrectly and you lose one life.
5. Guess correctly and a letter or letters will be revealed.

##Controls
- Click on-screen or your physical keyboard to guess the letters.
- Letters that have already been used will be unavailable.
- Use the Restart button to start a new game.
- Use the Home button to go back to main menu.

## Win Condition
- The player wins if they correctly and consecutively guess 6 words before their lives reach zero.

## Lose Condition
- The player loses if all lives are used.
- A system failure screen will show if you fail to defeat the viruses.

## Notes
- Words are randomly loaded from a text file.
- Players can input their own words to guess in the text file.
